            <thetext>Fixed with Revision #16632

In fact IE is not able to set the &quot;style&quot; attribute at all with the use of the element&#39;s &quot;setAttribute&quot; method.
Documented here: http://www.quirksmode.org/bugreports/archives/2005/03/setAttribute_does_not_work_in_IE_when_used_with_th.html

You have to use 

element.style.setAttribute(&quot;cssText&quot;, value)

to set the style values in IE.</thetext>
